0,174,0,0,7,""
0,174,1,0,2,"You will find my eggs in an old tomb not far from here. I'll help you defeat her then! But for now, bring me back my eggs. "
0,174,1,0,3,""
0,174,1,0,4,"Then our races will forever remain enemies. Too many precious words have been wasted on you! "
0,174,1,0,5,""
0,174,1,0,6,"You haven't brought my eggs back yet! Why haven't you? It's true what they say... yes, it's true after all! Humans are not to be trusted! You have betrayed a spider for the last time now. "
0,174,1,0,7,""
0,174,1,0,8,"My eggs! No longer shall I despair now, for a new beginning has been returned to me. I will tell you now how to defeat the Queen, human. She is weak to the flowing blue, to the rivers, the pools, the seas and the oceans. Water is her weakness, human. With that knowledge you should kill her and free us once and for all. Go now, and avenge the misery she has caused."
0,174,1,0,9,""
0,174,1,0,10,"Your help will not be forgotten, human."
